#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Pemecahan Masalah"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid ""
"If you are experiencing issues with OttoKit, clearing the cache will disconnect and re-connect your site. Your "
"automations and settings will be preserved."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda mengalami masalah dengan OttoKit, membersihkan cache akan memutuskan dan menyambungkan kembali situs Anda. "
"Automasi dan pengaturan Anda akan tetap terjaga."

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid "Clear Cache & Reconnect"
msgstr "Bersihkan Cache & Sambungkan Kembali"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid "When should you clear the cache?"
msgstr "Kapan Anda harus membersihkan cache?"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid "1. Connection issues after site migration"
msgstr "1. Masalah koneksi setelah migrasi situs"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid ""
"If you recently migrated your site to a new domain or hosting provider, the stored connection tokens may still point to "
"the old URL. Clearing the cache re-establishes the OttoKit connection with the new site URL so triggers and actions can "
"communicate correctly."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda baru-baru ini memigrasikan situs Anda ke domain atau penyedia hosting baru, token koneksi yang tersimpan "
"mungkin masih mengarah ke URL lama. Membersihkan cache membangun kembali koneksi OttoKit dengan URL situs baru sehingga "
"pemicu dan tindakan dapat berkomunikasi dengan benar."

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid "2. Automations suddenly stopped firing"
msgstr "2. Automasi tiba-tiba berhenti berfungsi"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid ""
"If your triggers and automations were working previously but have suddenly stopped, the authentication token or "
"registered events may have become stale. Clearing the cache refreshes the token, re-syncs all registered events with "
"the OttoKit server, and restores the connection."
msgstr ""
"Jika pemicu dan automasi Anda sebelumnya berfungsi tetapi tiba-tiba berhenti, token otentikasi atau acara yang "
"terdaftar mungkin telah kedaluwarsa. Membersihkan cache menyegarkan token, menyinkronkan ulang semua acara yang "
"terdaftar dengan server OttoKit, dan mengembalikan koneksi."

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid "3. Unexpected behavior after a plugin update"
msgstr "3. Perilaku tidak terduga setelah pembaruan plugin"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid ""
"After updating OttoKit (or related plugins like WooCommerce, LearnDash, etc.), cached data from the previous version "
"may cause triggers to not appear, events to not register, or the status page to show stale information. Clearing the "
"cache resolves these version mismatch issues."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memperbarui OttoKit (atau plugin terkait seperti WooCommerce, LearnDash, dll.), data yang di-cache dari versi "
"sebelumnya dapat menyebabkan pemicu tidak muncul, acara tidak terdaftar, atau halaman status menunjukkan informasi yang "
"kedaluwarsa. Membersihkan cache menyelesaikan masalah ketidakcocokan versi ini."

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-troubleshooting-page.php
msgid ""
"Clearing the cache will not delete your automations, settings, or connected integrations. It only resets the local "
"connection data so your site can re-authenticate with the OttoKit platform."
msgstr ""
"Membersihkan cache tidak akan menghapus automasi, pengaturan, atau integrasi yang terhubung. Ini hanya mereset data "
"koneksi lokal sehingga situs Anda dapat melakukan otentikasi ulang dengan platform OttoKit."

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-outgoing-req-page.php
msgid "Outgoing Request Logging"
msgstr "Pencatatan Permintaan Keluar"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-outgoing-req-page.php
msgid "Logging is currently disabled. No new requests are being stored. Failed requests cannot be retried automatically."
msgstr ""
"Pencatatan saat ini dinonaktifkan. Tidak ada permintaan baru yang disimpan. Permintaan yang gagal tidak dapat dicoba "
"ulang secara otomatis."

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-outgoing-req-page.php
msgid "Logging is enabled. Every outgoing webhook request is stored in the database for retry and history."
msgstr "Pencatatan diaktifkan. Setiap permintaan webhook keluar disimpan dalam database untuk percobaan ulang dan riwayat."

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-outgoing-req-page.php
msgid "Enable Logging"
msgstr "Aktifkan Pencatatan"

#: src/Admin/Views/st-admin-outgoing-req-page.php
msgid "Disable Logging"
msgstr "Nonaktifkan Pencatatan"

